FBIS4-29784 "dreas119_c_94001" FBIS-EAS-94-119 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song `Hopes To Hold' Mid-Aug Summit Kim Il-song `Hopes To Hold' Mid-Aug Summit OW2106055194 Tokyo KYODO in English 0531 GMT 21 Jun 94 OW2106055194 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Beijing, June 21 KYODO -- North Korean President Kim Il-song said he hopes to hold a summit meeting with South Korean President Kim Yong-sam in North Korea in mid-August, the widow of former Japanese Prime Minister Takeo Miki said Tuesday. Mutsuko Miki made the remarks to reporters at Beijing Airport after visiting North Korea. She met the North Korean leader Sunday.
